{{Quote|Come on, Keyan. Live dangerously. Take a chance. You've got to try the Mutandan porf.''"<br />"''Porf? Doesn't sound very good. What's in it?''"<br />"''Don't ask.|[[Hamo Blastwell]] and [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]]|<ref name="X-Wing: The Official Strategy Guide">''[[X-Wing: The Official Strategy Guide]]''</ref>}}
'''Mutandan porf''' was a blend of grain, meat, and spices from [[Mutanda]]. It was eaten with the hands and generally served with flat [[Bread/Legends|bread]]. One of the ingredients contained a mild stimulant. It was very filling but considered an acquired taste and was popular among the [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] serving onboard the [[Mon Calamari Star Cruiser/Legends|Mon Calamari Star Cruiser]] [[Independence/Legends|''Independence'']].

